quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  35,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  35,1,sab tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar hai ) jo asmano aur zameen ka peda karne wala ( aur ) firshton ko qasid bananay wala hai jin ke do do aur teen teen aur chaar chaar par hain. woh ( apni ) makhloqaat mein jo chahta hai berhata hai. be shak khuda har cheez par Qadir hai
  35,2,khuda jo apni rehmat ( ka darwaaza ) khol day to koi is ko band karne wala nahi. aur jo band kardey to is ke baad koi is ko kholnay wala nahi. aur woh ghalib hikmat wala hai
  35,3,logo khuda ke jo tum par ahsanat hain un ko yaad karo.kiya khuda ke siwa koi aur khaaliq ( aur Razaq hai ) jo tum ko aasman aur zameen se rizaq day. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi pas tum kahan behke phirtay ho ?
  35,4,aur ( ae paighambar ) agar yeh log tum koj hutla-ayn to tum se pehlay bhi paighambar jhutlaye gay-ay hain. aur ( sab ) kaam khuda hi ki taraf lout’tay jayen ge
  35,5,logo khuda ka wada sacha hai. to tum ko duniya ki zindagi dhokay mein nah daal day aur nah ( shetan ) fraib dainay wala tumhe fraib day
  35,6,shetan tumhara dushman hai tum bhi usay dushman hi samjhoo. woh apne ( پیروؤں ke ) giroh ko bulaataa hai taakay dozakh walon mein hon
  35,7,j_hnon ne kufarkiya un ke liye sakht azaab hai. aur jo imaan laaye aur amal naik karte rahay un ke liye bakhshish aur bara sawab hai
  35,8,bhala jis shakhs ko is ke aamaal bad aaraasta karkay dukhaay jayen aur woh un ko umdah samajhney lagey to (kiya woh nekokaar aadmi jaissa ho sakta hai ). be shak khuda jis ko chahta hai gumraah karta hai aur jis ko chahta hai hadaayat deta hai. to un logon par afsos karkay tumhara dam nah nikal jaye. yeh jo kuch karte hain khuda is se waaqif hai
  35,9,aur khuda hi to hai jo hawae chalata hai aur woh baadal ko abharti hain phir hum un ko aik be jaan shehar ki taraf chillate hain. phir is se zameen ko is ke marnay ke baad zindah kardete hain. isi terhan mardon ko jee uthna hoga
  35,10,jo shakhs izzat ka talab gaar hai to izzat to sab khuda hi ki hai. isi ki taraf pakeeza kalmaat charhtay hain aur naik amal is ko buland karte hain. aur jo log buray buray makr karte hain un ke liye sakht azaab hai. aur un ka makr nabood hojaye ga
  35,11,aur khuda hi ne tum ko matti se pedakiya phir nutfay se phir tum ko jora jora bana diya. aur koi aurat nah haamla hoti hai aur nah janati hai magar is ke ilm se. aur nah kisi barri Umar walay ko Umar ziyada di jati hai aur nah is ki Umar kam ki jati hai magar ( sab kuch ) kitaab mein ( likha howa ) hai. be shak yeh khuda ko aasaan hai
  35,12,aur dono darya ( mil kar ) yaksaa nahi ho jatay. yeh to meetha hai pyaas bujhanay wala. jis ka pani Khushgawar hai aur yeh khaari hai karva. aur sab se tum taaza gosht khatay ho aur zewar nikaltay ho jisay pehantay ho. aur tum darya mein kashtiyon ko dekhte ho ke ( pani ko ) pharti chali aati hain taakay tum is ke fazl se ( muaash ) talaash karo aur taakay shukar karo
  35,13,wohi raat ko din mein daakhil karta aur ( wohi ) din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai aur isi ne Sooraj aur chaand ko kaam mein laga diya hai. har aik aik waqt muqarrar taq chal raha hai. yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai isi ki badshahi hai. aur jin logon ko tum is ke siwa pkarte ho woh khajoor ki ghuthli ke chilkay ke barabar bhi to ( kisi cheez ke ) maalik nahi
  35,14,agar tum un ko poukaro to woh tumhari pukaar nah sunen aur agar sun bhi len to tumhari baat ko qubool nah kar saken. aur qayamat ke din tumahray shirk se inkaar kar dein ge. aur ( khuday-e ) bakhabar ki terhan tum ko koi khabar nahi day ga
  35,15,logo tum ( sab ) khuda ke mohtaaj ho aur khuda be parwa sazawar ( hamd وثنا ) hai
  35,16,agar chahay to tum ko nabood kardey aur nai makhloqaat laa abad kere
  35,17,aur yeh khuda ko kuch mushkil nahi
  35,18,aur koi uthany wala dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga. aur koi boojh mein daba howa apna boojh btane ko kisi ko bulaye to koi is mein se kuch nah uthaye ga agarchay qaraabat daar hi ho. ( ae paighambar ) tum unhi logon ko nasiyaat kar saktay ho jo ban dekhe apne perwar-digaar se drtay aur namaz balaltzam parhte hain. aur jo shakhs pak hota hai apne hi liye pak hota hai. aur ( sab ko ) khuda hi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
  35,19,aur andha aur aankhh wala barabar nahi
  35,20,aur nah andhera aur roshni
  35,21,aur nah saya aur dhoop
  35,22,aur nah zinday aur murdy barabar ho saktay hain. khuda jis ko chahta hai suna deta hai. aur tum un ko jo qabron mein madfoon hain nahi suna satke
  35,23,tum to sirf darane walay ho
  35,24,hum ne tum ko haq ke sath khushkhabri sunanay wala aur darane wala bheja hai. aur koi aُmt nahi magar is mein hadaayat karne wala guzar chuka hai
  35,25,aur agar yeh tumhari takzieeb karen to jo log un se pehlay they woh bhi takzieeb kar chukay hain un ke paas un ke paighambar nishanain aur saheefay aur roshan kitaaben le le kar atay rahay
  35,26,phir mein ne kafiroon ko pakar liya so ( dekh lau ke ) mera azaab kaisa howa
  35,27,kiya tum ne nahi dekha ke khuda ne aasman se meen barsaya. to hum ne is se terhan terhan ke rangon ke meway peda kiye. aur pahoron mein safaid aur surkh rangon ke qtaat hain aur ( baaz ) kalay siyah hain
  35,28,insanon aur janwaron aur charpayon ke bhi kayi terhan ke rang hain. khuda se to is ke bundon mein se wohi drtay hain jo sahib ilm hain. be shak khuda ghalib ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  35,29,jo log khuda ki kitaab parhte aur namaz ki pabandi karte hain aur jo kuch hum ne un ko diya hai is mein se posheeda aur zahir kharch karte hain woh is tijarat ( ke faiday ) ke umeed waar hain jo kabhi tabah nahi hogi
  35,30,kyunkay khuda un ko poora poora badla day ga aur apne fazl se kuch ziyada bhi day ga. woh to bakhsnay wala ( aur ) qadar daan hai
  35,31,aur yeh kitaab jo hum ne tumhari taraf bhaije hai brhq hai. aur un ( kitabon ) ki tasdeeq karti hai jo is se pehlay ki hain. be shak khuda apne bundon se khabardaar ( aur un ko ) dekhnay wala hai
  35,32,phir hum ne un logon ko kitaab ka waris tehraya jin ko apne bundon mein se bargzidakiya. to kuch to un mein se apne aap par zulm karte hain. aur kuch miyana ro hain. aur kuch khuda ke hukum se nakiyon mein agay nikal jaane walay hain. yahi bara fazl hai
  35,33,( un logon ke liye ) bahisht javedani ( hain ) jin mein woh daakhil hon ge. wahan un ko sonay ke kangon aur moti pahnaye jayen ge. aur un ki poshak reshmi hogi
  35,34,woh kahin ge ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne hum se gham daurkiya. be shak hamara perwar-digaar bakhsnay wala ( aur ) qadar daan hai
  35,35,jis ne hum ko apne fazl se hamesha ke rehne ke ghar mein utaara. yahan nah to hum ko ranj puhanche ga aur nah hamein takan hi hogi
  35,36,aur jin logon ne kufarkiya un ke liye dozakh ki aag hai. nah inhen mout aeye gi ke mrjayin aur nah un ka azaab hi un se halkakiya jaye ga. hum har aik nashukray ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
  35,37,woh is mein chalayein ge ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko nikaal le ( ab ) hum naik amalkiya karen ge. nah woh jo ( pehlay ) karte they.kiya hum ne tum ko itni Umar nahi di thi ke is mein jo sochna chahta soch laita aur tumahray paas darane wala bhi aaya. to ab mazay chako. zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi
  35,38,be shak khuda hi asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baton ka jan-nay wala hai. woh to dil ke bheidoon taq se waaqif hai
  35,39,wohi to hai jis ne tum ko zameen mein ( pehloo ka ) janasheen banaya. to jis ne kufarkiya is ke kufar ka zarrar isi ko hai. aur kafiroon ke haq mein un ke kufar se perwar-digaar ke haan na khushi hi barhti hai aur kafiroon ko un ka kufar nuqsaan hi ziyada karta hai
  35,40,bhala tum ne apne sharikon ko dekha jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho. mujhe dikhao ke unhon ne zameen se kon si cheez peda ki hai ya ( batao ke ) asmano mein un ki shirkat hai. ya hum ne un ko kitaab di hai to woh is ki sanad rakhtay hain ( un mein se koi baat bhi nahi ) balkay zalim jo aik dosray ko wada dete hain mehez fraib hai
  35,41,khuda hi asmano aur zameen ko thaamay rakhta hai ke tal nah jayen. agar woh tal jayen to khuda ke siwa koi aisa nahi jo un ko thaam sakay. be shak woh Burdbar ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  35,42,aur yeh khuda ki sakht sakht kasmain khatay hain ke agar un ke paas koi hadaayat karne wala aeye to har aik aُmt se barh kar hadaayat par hon. magar jab un ke paas hadaayat karne wala aaya to is se un ko nafrat hi barhi
  35,43,yani ( unhon ne ) malik mein ghuroor karna aur buri chaal chalna ( ikhtiyarkiya ) aur buri chaal ka wabaal is ke chalne walay hi par parta hai. yeh aglay logon ki rawish ke siwa aur kisi cheez ke munhtazir nahi. so tum khuda ki aadat mein hargiz Tabdal nah pao ge. aur khuda ke tareeqay mein kabhi tagayur nah dekho ge
  35,44,kiya unhon ne zameen mein kabhi sair nahi ki taakay dekhte ke jo log un se pehlay they un ka injaamkiya howa halaank woh un se qowat mein bohat ziyada they. aur khuda aisa nahi ke asmano aur zameen mein koi cheez is ko aajiz kar sakay. woh ilm wala ( aur ) qudrat wala hai
  35,45,aur agar khuda logon ko un ke aamaal ke sabab pakarney lagta. to roye zameen par aik chalne phirnay walay ko nah chhorta. lekin woh un ko aik waqt muqarrar taq mohlat diye jata hai. so jab un ka waqt aajay ga to ( un ke aamaal ka badla day ga ) khuda to apne bundon ko dekh raha hai
